## MindLang AI 에이전트: 프레임워크 (TypeScript)

**목표**: MindLang 에이전트를 실제로 실행하는 TypeScript 프레임워크

### 1. agent-framework.ts (600줄)
MindLang 에이전트 런타임:

```typescript
// 에이전트 상태 관리
class MindLangAgent {
  private state: AgentState
  private vm: VirtualMachine
  private mindlangProgram: string

  constructor(mindlangPath: string) {
    this.vm = new VirtualMachine()
    this.mindlangProgram = loadMindLangFile(mindlangPath)
  }

  // 메인 에이전트 실행
  async think(query: string): Promise<AgentResponse> {
    // 1. MindLang 프로그램 컴파일
    const bytecode = compileToMindLang(this.mindlangProgram)

    // 2. 질문을 벡터로 인코딩
    const q = encodeQuery(query)

    // 3. VM 실행
    const z = this.vm.execute(bytecode, {query: q})

    // 4. 3가지 경로 병렬 실행
    const [z_a, z_b, z_c] = await Promise.all([
      this.vm.executeAnalytical(z),
      this.vm.executeCreative(z),
      this.vm.executeEmpirical(z)
    ])

    // 5. 적응형 가중치
    const weights = computeAdaptiveWeights(query, [z_a, z_b, z_c])

    // 6. 앙상블
    const ensemble = weightedEnsemble(weights, [z_a, z_b, z_c])

    // 7. 자가 비판
    const critique = selfCritique(ensemble, query)

    // 8. 샘플링 및 출력
    if (critique.confidence > 0.8) {
      return {
        response: detokenizeKorean(ensemble),
        confidence: critique.confidence,
        reasoning: {
          analytical: z_a,
          creative: z_b,
          empirical: z_c,
          weights: weights,
          critique: critique
        }
      }
    } else {
      return await this.retryWithFeedback(query, critique)
    }
  }

  // 피드백으로 재시도
  private async retryWithFeedback(
    query: string, 
    critique: Critique
  ): Promise<AgentResponse> {
    const improvedQuery = query + " [feedback: " + critique.feedback + "]"
    return this.think(improvedQuery)
  }
}
```

### 2. agent-compiler.ts (300줄)
MindLang 에이전트 컴파일러:

```typescript
class MindLangAgentCompiler {
  compile(agentCode: string): CompiledAgent {
    // 1. Parse MindLang 에이전트
    const ast = parseMindLang(agentCode)

    // 2. Type check
    const typedAST = typeCheck(ast)

    // 3. Extract paths
    const analyticalPath = extractPath(typedAST, 'analytical')
    const creativePath = extractPath(typedAST, 'creative')
    const empiricalPath = extractPath(typedAST, 'empirical')

    // 4. Compile to bytecode
    const analyticalBC = compile(analyticalPath)
    const creativeBC = compile(creativePath)
    const empiricalBC = compile(empiricalPath)

    return {
      analytical: analyticalBC,
      creative: creativeBC,
      empirical: empiricalBC,
      weights: extractWeights(typedAST),
      critique: extractCritique(typedAST)
    }
  }
}
```

### 3. agent-executor.ts (300줄)
에이전트 실행 엔진:

```typescript
class AgentExecutor {
  // 3가지 경로 동시 실행
  async executeParallel(
    q: Vector,
    compiled: CompiledAgent
  ): Promise<ParallelResults> {
    const startTime = Date.now()

    const [analytical, creative, empirical] = await Promise.all([
      this.executeAnalytical(q, compiled.analytical),
      this.executeCreative(q, compiled.creative),
      this.executeEmpirical(q, compiled.empirical)
    ])

    return {
      analytical: { result: analytical, time: Date.now() - startTime },
      creative: { result: creative, time: Date.now() - startTime },
      empirical: { result: empirical, time: Date.now() - startTime },
      totalTime: Date.now() - startTime
    }
  }

  // 적응형 가중치 계산
  computeAdaptiveWeights(
    query: string,
    results: ParallelResults
  ): Weights {
    // 질문 유형 분석
    const queryType = analyzeQueryType(query)

    // 각 경로의 신뢰도
    const confidences = {
      analytical: assessAnalytical(results.analytical),
      creative: assessCreative(results.creative),
      empirical: assessEmpirical(results.empirical)
    }

    // 질문 유형에 따른 가중치
    return adaptWeights(queryType, confidences)
  }

  // 자가 비판
  async selfCritique(
    ensemble: Vector,
    originalQuery: string
  ): Promise<Critique> {
    return {
      confidence: calculateConfidence(ensemble),
      strengths: identifyStrengths(ensemble),
      weaknesses: identifyWeaknesses(ensemble),
      feedback: generateFeedback(ensemble, originalQuery),
      shouldRetry: shouldRetry(ensemble)
    }
  }
}
```

### 4. agent-integrations.ts (200줄)
외부 시스템 통합:

```typescript
// MindLang 에이전트와 기존 시스템 통합
interface AgentIntegration {
  // FreeLang v4 코드 검증
  validateCodeWithFreeLang(code: string): ValidationResult

  // Claude API 호출
  callClaudeAPI(prompt: string): Promise<string>

  // 데이터베이스 조회
  queryDatabase(sql: string): Promise<any[]>

  // 외부 API 호출
  callExternalAPI(url: string, options: any): Promise<any>

  // 메모리/캐시 관리
  getCachedResult(key: string): any | null
  setCachedResult(key: string, value: any): void
}
```

